      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in a truly preserved state. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring a proactively reinforced rear subframe and pristine factory bushings. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a GKN variable M-differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Comprehensive mechanical provenance includes documented rod bearing replacement and VANOS hub overhaul. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turn-key, concours-ready example for the discerning collector.",
