      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem for the discerning enthusiast: a truly pristine example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, featuring deep, lustrous paint that has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for a mirror-like shine. You will find zero stone chips, dings, or swirl marks across the entire body. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no softening or bolster wear, the original factory scent remains, and every digital display and switch functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is concours-level clean, the undercarriage is free of debris, and the wheels are entirely devoid of curb rash. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule quality vehicle. It comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick binder of service documentation.",
